summary: This document is a summary of a VTC (Video Teleconference) preparation session between an AUSA (Assistant United States Attorney) and a Detective/Special Agent regarding the October 20, 2005 search of Jeffrey Epstein's property at 358 El Brillo Way. The witness reviewed and confirmed recognition of numerous photographic and video exhibits from the search, including a green massage table seized from the master bathroom.

keyFacts: A green massage table was seized from the master bathroom during the October 20, 2005 search of 358 El Brillo Way.
The document details extensive photographic and video evidence (exhibits GX-201 through GX-299) from the 2005 search, covering exterior, interior, first floor, second floor, and kitchen areas.
The preparation occurred on November 15, 2021, indicating ongoing legal proceedings related to the Epstein case at that time.
The document is subject to a protective order restricting certain paragraphs.
